{"tid":1058423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本遊戲迷新婚夫婦 為婚禮自製出 RPG 遊戲","createTime":"2019-03-12T13:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T16:36:49.000Z","uid":75969,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"237f4862562f3bf0968cda2033047da0b9cba559","tid":1058423,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1OVsELU4AEuGVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1OVsELU4AEuGVG.jpg&h=45c5bd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1YaCflU4AA-LPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1YaCflU4AA-LPE.jpg&h=4f9f3994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山口翼夫婦兩人都非常喜歡遊戲，他們想有一個特別的婚禮，因此就有了這個構想，他們以初代 PS 平台 RPG 遊戲的風格，造出了一段介紹他們兩人的遊戲 OP。最後更造出了一隻以他們兩人婚禮題材的 RPG 遊戲，來場的賓客更可以透過手機遊玩！<br />\n<br />\nOP<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/322778481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F322778481&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0LazKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=c50c8502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/322778481</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1YaCflUYAEB1CL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1YaCflUYAEB1CL.jpg&h=3d27f4d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，職業是漫畫家的山口翼更事先對來場的賓客做了問卷調查，詢問他們想在 RPG 遊戲做的職業，再以他們的特徵為總數 70 名以上的來賓設計了他們的 RPG 角色形象，再製成了一本賓客名冊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1YaCfpV4AAIUoq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1YaCfpV4AAIUoq.jpg&h=d45ea3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1YaCf5UYAAx_lI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1YaCf5UYAAx_lI.jpg&h=3b406d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就連他們婚禮的請帖和結婚蛋糕也是以 PlayStation 來設計，非常具心思。這個一生一次的婚禮絕對成為他們最難忘的回憶！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1Ye-yKVAAETdKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1Ye-yKVAAETdKt.jpg&h=a1a4eb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1Ye-yKUYAEiwEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1Ye-yKUYAEiwEY.jpg&h=60e433fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201903/12/D1Ye-yHUYAAl0xi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201903%2F12%2FD1Ye-yHUYAAl0xi.jpg&h=1da87814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/32547/RPG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F32547%2FRPG&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0LazKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=4130dcba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/32547/RPG</a>"},{"pid":"3fb16a5e63c1c4234078b5109c818ec7b897fdd2","tid":1058423,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":92,"score":-91,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"睇下幾時game over <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96436d30112a8801eb883faf51473d68c3512558","tid":1058423,"uid":3764,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"3fb16a5e63c1c4234078b5109c818ec7b897fdd2","tid":1058423,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":92,"score":-91,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"睇下幾時game over <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"想收負評咪岀聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bde305bdfa85763194539ab72389f29551fb01","tid":1058423,"uid":210851,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy